## What’s inside

- `wfpack.yaml` (pack manifest)
- `{{component_path}}` (main component)
- `skill/instructions.md` (canonical skill instructions, optional)
- `applet/` (static UI, optional)

## Build

```bash
wayfinder pack fmt --path .
wayfinder pack doctor --path .
wayfinder pack render-skill --path .
wayfinder pack build --path . --out dist/bundle.zip
```

## Publish

```bash
export WAYFINDER_PACKS_API_URL="https://strategies-dev.wayfinder.ai"
export WAYFINDER_API_KEY="wk_..."
wayfinder pack publish --path .
```

For bonded publishes:

```bash
wayfinder pack publish --path . --bonded --owner-wallet 0xYourWallet --risk-tier execution
```

`wayfinder pack publish` builds `bundle.zip` and `source.zip`, generates thin skill exports when this pack has a skill, requests signed upload URLs from the Packs API, uploads artifacts directly to storage, then finalizes the submission and prints a manage URL plus the next required action.
